It was first reported in 1973 by N. Bilginturan et al.<ref>{{cite journal |last=Chitayat |first=D. |last2=Grix |first2=A. |last3=Balfe |first3=J. W. |last4=Abramowicz |first4=J. S. |last5=Garza |first5=J. |last6=Fong |first6=C. T. |last7=Silver |first7=M. M. |last8=Saller |first8=D. N. |last9=Bresnick |first9=G. H. |date=1997-12-19 |title=Brachydactyly-short stature-hypertension (Bilginturan) syndrome: report on two families |journal=American Journal of Medical Genetics |volume=73 |issue=3 |pages=279–285 |issn=0148-7299 |pmid=9415685}}</ref><ref>{{cite journal |last=Bilginturan |first=N. |last2=Zileli |first2=S. |last3=Karacadag |first3=S. |last4=Pirnar |first4=T. |date=1973-09-01 |title=Hereditary Brachydactyly Associated with Hypertension |journal=Journal of Medical Genetics |volume=10 |issue=3 |pages=253–259 |issn=0022-2593 |pmc=1013029 |pmid=4774535}}</ref> The estimated prevalence is less than 1 out of 1,000,000.<ref name=":1" />
== Symptoms == The disorder is characterized by: * severe salt-independent but age-dependent [[hypertension]] * [[brachydactyly]] malformations of the hands and fingers * increased [[fibroblast]] growth rate * neurovascular contact at the rostral-ventrolateral medulla * altered [[baroreflex]] blood pressure regulation * death from [[stroke]] before age 50 years when untreated == Genetics == The disorder is thought to be related to mutations in the [[Phosphodiesterase 3|PDE3A]] gene.<ref name=":0" /><ref>{{cite journal |last=Maass |first=Philipp G. |last2=Aydin |first2=Atakan |last3=Luft |first3=Friedrich C. |last4=Schächterle |first4=Carolin |last5=Weise |first5=Anja |last6=Stricker |first6=Sigmar |last7=Lindschau |first7=Carsten |last8=Vaegler |first8=Martin |last9=Qadri |first9=Fatimunnisa |date=2015-06-01 |title=PDE3A mutations cause autosomal dominant hypertension with brachydactyly |journal=Nature Genetics |volume=47 |issue=6 |pages=647–653 |doi=10.1038/ng.3302 |issn=1546-1718 |pmid=25961942}}</ref> ==Diagnosis== {{Empty section|date=January 2018}} ==Treatment== {{Empty section|date=January 2018}}
